{"tid":852761,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇小猁猁同我一樣 睇完琴晚場波開始有啲掛住張伯伯？","createTime":"2018-10-08T05:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T09:08:17.000Z","uid":147389,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"71bb4cf89711f34e63b7998f5a655c3bf7d2f2b6","tid":852761,"uid":147389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"助攻助守 有活力 體能 體格 速度 突破能力 <br />\n可以由後場帶波上去 有佢喺度打反擊又多一個點<br />\n進攻嗰陣有時可以將佢拉去偏向右邊 將沙拿移入中間少少 咁樣邊路多一個突破點 同時可以牽引對手 減輕沙拿壓力<br />\n仲有...遠射能力 係而家利記所缺乏嘅嘢<br />\n仲記得上年對曼城入嗰兩球遠射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f308953850ebdab57ee762080e436a4487ab72d9","tid":852761,"uid":147389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推 唔通真係得我一個掛住張伯伯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be041b2362e040ccdf17c90e0a51e58e9f42cca5","tid":852761,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"On9子一日唔改名<br />\n佢一日都唔會好返"},{"pid":"e2661692dff4dbb6558c948d3e48bc04e30217e3","tid":852761,"uid":147389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:02:50.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"7d8a8524cdfd27715d05726cc22ced7fa8f7eee8","tid":852761,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be041b2362e040ccdf17c90e0a51e58e9f42cca5","tid":852761,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"On9子一日唔改名<br />\n佢一日都唔會好返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb5d73e47ccf054390cd0fa55909939d1d54bbe","tid":852761,"uid":147389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}